title: The List with Colleen Lopez 08.10.2017 - 09 PM
description:
This coming fall season is all about the design details from head to toe. Embroidered and embellished items from Steven by Steve Madden, Deepa Gurnani, and more! Curator and host Colleen Lopez takes the guesswork out of style by showcasing her weekly favorites.
Prices shown on the previously recorded video may not represent the current price. Visit http://www.hsn.com to view the current selling price.
